    <item>
      <title>亚洲债券销售迎来一年中最繁忙的一天，推动全球繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/philippines-offers-dollar-bonds-including-sustainability-notes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球债券发行热潮在亚洲蓄势待发，至少有五家借款人排队发行债券，这使其成为该地区自 2023 年 6 月以来最繁忙的一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/philippines-offers-dollar-bonds-including-sustainability-notes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 02:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
